-- William Hill CEO Says Talks With Playtech Are Progessing Well
-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 2012-04-20T09:04:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-20/william-hill-ceo-says-talks-with-playtech-are-progessing-well.html
William Hill Plc (WMH)  Chief Executive
Officer Ralph Topping said talks with  Playtech Ltd. (PTEC)  are
progressing well and will continue over the summer.  “Talks are going extremely well,” Topping said on a
conference call with analysts today, adding the company will
update investors in the summer.  William Hill started talks in March with Playtech, a
minority shareheolder in William Hill Online, on whether to end
their joint venture or find a “third way” after a breakdowm in
relations last year, the Financial Times reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
